            "title": "Beware of the Trees",
            "summary": "Another image where i put a character in a somewhat surreal scene,&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/7/gallery/ComfyUI_00445_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/7/gallery/ComfyUI_00445_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/7/gallery/beware-of-the-trees-large.jpg\" data-size=\"461x600\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/7/gallery/beware-of-the-trees-large-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"600\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>Another image where i put a character in a somewhat surreal scene, I look forward to making the video animation for this image. I used AI to lightly apply color while maintaining the general composition of the original image.</p>",
