        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/double-dribble.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/double-dribble.html",
            "title": "Double Dribble",
            "summary": "This is an old sketch and I thought this would be a&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/6/gallery/scan0040.jpg\" data-size=\"407x600\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/6/gallery/scan0040-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"407\" height=\"600\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/6/gallery/ComfyUI_00621_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/6/gallery/ComfyUI_00621_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/6/gallery/ComfyUI_00620_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/6/gallery/ComfyUI_00620_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is an old sketch and I thought this would be a perfect test of what could be done with an advanced AI edit model. For this picture I was curious if it could take my bad drawing and keep the pose but also make a coherent image. I also tested how much of the original concept could be kept as a reference while making a new concept slightly modifying the rough areas</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/6/ComfyUI_00621_.png",
