        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/the-a-team.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/the-a-team.html",
            "title": "The A Team",
            "summary": "This is a sketch i made when i was around 5. I&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/5/gallery/20251106_023529-2.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/5/gallery/20251106_023529-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/5/gallery/ComfyUI_00476_-2.png\" data-size=\"1656x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/5/gallery/ComfyUI_00476_-2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"575\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is a sketch i made when i was around 5. I have laughed at myself for many years with this picture I made so very long ago. This was a fun one to feed to AI and see something so old brought to a new life. This was one of my first tests with AI edit models and I told it this was a movie poster and it added text mock up spots. I have since learned alot but both of these are sentimental : )</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/5/ComfyUI_00476_.png",
