        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/we-come-in-peace.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/we-come-in-peace.html",
            "title": "We Come in Peace",
            "summary": "I always love surreal, image within image kind of concepts even while&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/4/gallery/ComfyUI_00452_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/4/gallery/ComfyUI_00452_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/4/gallery/scan0020.jpg\" data-size=\"1166x1938\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/4/gallery/scan0020-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1276\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>I always love surreal, image within image kind of concepts even while working on characters, so its was fun to feed the black and white image to AI and see it brought to life.</p>",
