            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/3/gallery/scan0053.jpg\" data-size=\"411x600\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/3/gallery/scan0053-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"411\" height=\"600\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/3/gallery/ComfyUI_00440_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/3/gallery/ComfyUI_00440_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>Just some fun while learning about about the new tech with my old artwork. For this experiment I tested the model ability to make a paint texture. The original is has less color.</p>",
